code: @Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     out.writeList(infos). }

@Override public XContentBuilder toXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     builder.startObject(Fields.THREAD_POOL).     for (ThreadPool.Info info : infos) {         info.toXContent(builder, params).     }     builder.endObject().     return builder. }
